        public int[] getFrameBoundsAt(long position)
        Returns the information for the frame at stream position.
        Parameters:
        position - Position in milliseconds
        Returns:
        An int-array containing the bounds and URL where the indexes are specified as followed:
        • 0: Index of the URL
        • 1: Left bound
        • 2: Top bound
        • 3: Right bound
        • 4: Bottom bound
